  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌊 Submeris</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651940/extras/d5178134be2a38f085a859fef484b643.poster.avif?t=1745664623\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651940/extras/d5178134be2a38f085a859fef484b643.webm?t=1745664623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651940/extras/d5178134be2a38f085a859fef484b643.mp4?t=1745664623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A deep-sea mining adventure filled with exploration, danger, and survival beneath a mysterious island!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Dig. Upgrade. Descend. And uncover the treasure buried deep below.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >---</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎮 About the Game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Submeris</strong> invites you into an immersive underwater experience combining <strong>exploration</strong>, <strong>mining mechanics</strong>, and <strong>survival gameplay</strong> beneath a remote and mysterious island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start with just a simple shovel. Level up, upgrade your gear, and dive deeper into the unknown. But beware — limited oxygen, rising radiation, collapsing tunnels, and <strong>deadly sharks</strong> all stand between you and the ultimate treasure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The deeper you go, the greater the reward — and the risk.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >---</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚒️ Dig – Upgrade – Descend</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upgrade your shovel and pickaxe</strong> – dig faster and break stronger materials</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651940/extras/d7a2997ac294bd5490e727efbc9259af.poster.avif?t=1745664623\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651940/extras/d7a2997ac294bd5490e727efbc9259af.webm?t=1745664623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651940/extras/d7a2997ac294bd5490e727efbc9259af.mp4?t=1745664623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use dynamite and tools</strong> – break through obstacles and discover new paths</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651940/extras/ce531e7e8d8f112ab3145e4f813a391c.poster.avif?t=1745664623\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651940/extras/ce531e7e8d8f112ab3145e4f813a391c.webm?t=1745664623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651940/extras/ce531e7e8d8f112ab3145e4f813a391c.mp4?t=1745664623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use the detector</strong> – locate buried treasures and hidden cash beneath the ocean floor</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651940/extras/d1c58a3b79fac3ab90f1362733276591.poster.avif?t=1745664623\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651940/extras/d1c58a3b79fac3ab90f1362733276591.webm?t=1745664623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651940/extras/d1c58a3b79fac3ab90f1362733276591.mp4?t=1745664623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enhance your light source</strong> – illuminate dark tunnels below</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651940/extras/75b01eec6f71544834c2927b213b91a1.poster.avif?t=1745664623\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651940/extras/75b01eec6f71544834c2927b213b91a1.webm?t=1745664623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651940/extras/75b01eec6f71544834c2927b213b91a1.mp4?t=1745664623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Expand your inventory</strong> – carry more loot, earn more profit</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651940/extras/eb7f4f2e891e927a870d8ec914fa7289.poster.avif?t=1745664623\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651940/extras/eb7f4f2e891e927a870d8ec914fa7289.webm?t=1745664623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651940/extras/eb7f4f2e891e927a870d8ec914fa7289.mp4?t=1745664623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Boost oxygen and radiation resistance</strong> – dive longer and go deeper</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651940/extras/f21870e2d3401907a892da9aaa96ae72.poster.avif?t=1745664623\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651940/extras/f21870e2d3401907a892da9aaa96ae72.webm?t=1745664623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651940/extras/f21870e2d3401907a892da9aaa96ae72.mp4?t=1745664623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >---</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >💰 High Risk, Greater Reward</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the depths, <strong>precious minerals</strong>, <strong>hidden chests</strong>, and <strong>legendary treasures</strong> await. But only the most prepared divers can survive the hazards below.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Radiation zones with time pressure  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unstable tunnels at risk of collapse  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And most dangerously — <strong>sharks guarding the final treasure</strong>  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Every layer hides danger, but also opportunity.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >---</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎯 Who Is This Game For?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Submeris</strong> is made for players who enjoy:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmospheric exploration  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mining and digging gameplay  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survival and resource management  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progression through risk vs reward  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dark, mysterious underwater environments  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >---</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🚀 Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Depth-based leveling and progression system  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgradeable tools: shovel, pickaxe, lamp, dynamite, inventory  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategic survival with oxygen & radiation mechanics  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sell valuable minerals and discover rare treasures  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock secret rooms, loot hidden chests, survive deadly encounters  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Realistic underwater atmosphere and dynamic lighting system  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shark threats in deep treasure zones  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >---</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔚 Ready to dive deep? Hold your breath... and descend.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>“True treasure lies only where the bold dare to go.”</i></p>",
